room_title: Escape room "Bates Motel" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
review: This was our first experience and by far the absolute best. It is challenging and definitely allows you to work as a TEAM with the people you bring. We will be coming back for another more challenging room. Bates Motel is awesome!

room_title: Escape room "Bates Motel" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
review: We had so much fun and escaped Bates Motel! Definitely the best escape room we have visited.

room_title: Escape room "Bates Motel" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
review: Awesome time escaping the Bates Motel and from Norman! It was a close one, but we prevailed. Best room by far! We will be back! Try Longview’s Escape room, too! Same owners and great rooms as well.

room_title: Escape room "Bates Motel" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
review: We completed Bates Motel and loved it! Seriously a great experience and worth the time and money. We’ll go back for sure!!!

room_title: Escape room "Bates Motel" by Tyler Escape Room in Tyler
review: Lots of fun. The staff was friendly, helpful and very welcoming. We tried the new Bates Motel themed room, and were not disappointed. It's definitely a fun way to spend an afternoon or evening with friends and/or family. We will be going back to try some of the other settings.
